---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NavLinkShowcase from '../components/NavLinkShowcase.astro';
---

<Layout title="Your Journey" description="Discover how we craft your bespoke Bali experience through soul discovery, intention mapping, and personalized curation.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center bg-stone-900 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-stone-900/60 via-stone-900/40 to-stone-900/80 z-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/adventure/banyan-tree-walk.webp')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="hero-animate text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">The Bespoke Process</p>
      <h1 class="hero-animate hero-animate-delay-1 font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-stone-50 leading-tight">
        How Your Journey<br/>Takes Shape
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="prose-luxury reveal">
        <p>
          A journey with Bali Encore begins long before you arrive on the island. 
          It begins with a conversation—a careful, unhurried exploration of who you 
          are, what you seek, and what transformation awaits you. From this foundation, 
          we craft an experience that exists for you alone.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Step 1: Soul Discovery -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-125 reveal-scale image-reveal">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/temples/village-shrine.webp')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full border-2 border-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-gold-600">01</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-1">First Step</p>
              <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-900">Soul Discovery</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="prose-luxury">
            <p>
              Every meaningful journey begins with understanding. Before we discuss 
              destinations or experiences, we seek to know you—not just your preferences, 
              but your essence.
            </p>
            <p>
              Through intimate conversation, we explore the questions that matter: 
              What brings you to this moment? What have you been seeking that ordinary 
              travel cannot provide? What would it mean to return home transformed?
            </p>
            <p>
              This is not a questionnaire. It is a dialogue—a meeting of minds and 
              intentions that forms the foundation of everything to come.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Step 2: Intention Mapping -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full border-2 border-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-gold-600">02</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-1">Second Step</p>
              <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-900">Intention Mapping</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="prose-luxury">
            <p>
              From the seeds of our conversation, we begin to map the terrain of 
              your journey. Not a rigid itinerary, but a constellation of possibilities 
              aligned with your deepest intentions.
            </p>
            <p>
              Perhaps you seek spiritual awakening—we identify the sacred spaces and 
              teachers who can guide you. Perhaps you crave adventure that challenges 
              and transforms—we chart the paths less traveled. Perhaps you long for 
              cultural immersion that changes how you see the world—we open doors 
              that remain closed to ordinary travelers.
            </p>
            <p>
              Your intention becomes our compass. Every element we consider must 
              serve the journey you are meant to take.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative h-125 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/nature/waterfall-couple.webp')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Step 3: Experience Curation -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-125">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/culture/tirta-gangga.webp')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full border-2 border-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-gold-600">03</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-1">Third Step</p>
              <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-900">Experience Curation</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="prose-luxury">
            <p>
              Now the artistry begins. Drawing from our deep relationships with 
              Bali's most extraordinary places, people, and practices, we curate 
              experiences that resonate with your mapped intentions.
            </p>
            <p>
              A private ceremony with a high priest. A sunrise trek to a temple 
              known only to locals. An afternoon with a master artisan who has 
              never taught an outsider. A meal prepared by hands that have cooked 
              for royalty.
            </p>
            <p>
              Each experience is selected not for its impressiveness, but for its 
              alignment with your journey. We seek resonance, not spectacle.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Step 4: Journey Design -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full border-2 border-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-gold-600">04</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-1">Fourth Step</p>
              <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-900">Journey Design</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="prose-luxury">
            <p>
              The curated experiences are woven into a coherent journey—a narrative 
              arc that honors the rhythm of transformation. We consider not just 
              what you will do, but how each day flows into the next.
            </p>
            <p>
              Moments of intensity are balanced with spaces for integration. 
              Adventure is followed by stillness. Outward exploration gives way 
              to inward reflection. The design serves the deeper purpose.
            </p>
            <p>
              We present this design to you not as a fixed plan, but as a living 
              proposal—open to refinement, responsive to your intuition, ready 
              to evolve as your journey unfolds.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative h-125 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/adventure/jungle-descent.webp')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Step 5: Personal Host & Concierge -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-900 text-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-125">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/adventure/forest-walk.webp')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full border-2 border-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-gold-500">05</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gold-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-1">Fifth Step</p>
              <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-stone-50">Personal Host & Concierge</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              From the moment you arrive until the moment you depart, you are 
              accompanied by a dedicated personal host—not a guide who recites 
              facts, but a companion who understands your journey and ensures 
              every moment serves it.
            </p>
            <p>
              Your host is your bridge to Bali—fluent in the island's languages, 
              customs, and hidden treasures. They anticipate needs before they 
              arise. They create space when you need solitude and connection 
              when you seek company.
            </p>
            <p>
              Behind your host stands our full concierge team, available around 
              the clock to handle any request, adjust any plan, and ensure that 
              nothing interrupts the flow of your transformation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Summary -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-gold-600 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">The Promise</p>
      <div class="divider divider-center mb-12"></div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-900 mb-12">
        A Journey Unlike Any Other
      </h2>
      
      <div class="prose-luxury text-center">
        <p>
          This is what it means to journey with Bali Encore. Not a tour. Not a 
          vacation. Not an escape from life, but a deeper entry into it. A 
          carefully crafted passage from who you are to who you are becoming.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every detail considered. Every moment intentional. Every experience 
          chosen because it speaks to something within you that is ready to awaken.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <NavLinkShowcase heading="Reconnect with Our Core Pages" theme="light" />

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/hero/hero-nature.webp')] bg-cover bg-center bg-fixed"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-stone-900/70"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-6">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-50 mb-8">
        Ready to Begin?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-stone-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        The first step is a conversation. Tell us who you are and what you seek.
      </p>
      <a href="/begin" class="btn-luxury-outline">Start Your Journey</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
